openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API Overview
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  "/":
    get:
      operationId: listVersionsv2
      summary: List API versions
      responses:
        "200":
          description: 200 response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                foo:
                  value:
                    versions:
                      - status: CURRENT
                        updated: "2011-01-21T11:33:21Z"
                        id: v2.0
                        links:
                          - href: http://127.0.0.1:8774/v2/
                            rel: self
components:
  responses:
    ResponseExample:
      description: 200 response
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: object
            discriminator:
              propertyName: petType
            properties:
              code:
                type: string
                format: binary
              message:
                type: string
          encoding:
            profileImage:
              headers:
                Content-Type:
                  contentType: image/png, image/jpeg
